<h1>Your Question is Ready</h1>

<div class="para">The link to share for expressing preferences is:</div>
<div>
  <a class="displayLink" href="<%= choice_path(@choice.read_token) %>"
  >Click here to see your question. Copy this link to share!</a>
</div>
<div>Most browsers will allow
you to right click on the link and copy to your clipboard in order to
paste the link elsewhere, to publish.
</div>

<div class="para">The link for viewing the result will be:</div>
<div>
<a class="displayLink" href="<%= result_choice_path(@choice.read_token) %>"
>View result of question, <%= @choice.title %></a>
</div>

<div class="para">To edit your choice before anyone has expressed a preference,
go to:</div>
<div>
<a class="displayLink" href="<%= edit_choice_path(@choice.edit_token) %>"
>Click here to edit your question, <%= @choice.title %></a>
</div>

<%= render :partial => 'display', :object => @choice %>

<%= home_button %>
